# File

## Writing Files

search
  [#file/write path contents]
watch file/write
  (path, contents)
end

## Reading Files

search
  f = [#file/read path]
watch file/read
  (f, path)
end

When a file read change event comes around, set the contents of the file.

search
  t = [#file/read/change file contents]
  file = [#file/read]
commit
  file.contents := contents
end